{"word":"G1336 - διηνεκής - diēnekḗs - dee-ay-nek-es' - + continually","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διηνεκής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diēnekḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ay-nek-es'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">+ continually</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நிலைத்திருக்கிற, இடைவிடாத, என்றென்றைக்கும் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"continuous"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and a derivative of an alternate of <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a>; <i>carried through</i>, that is, (adverb with <a href=\"#/G1519 - εἰς - eis - ice/1519\">G1519</a> and <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a> prefixed) <i>perpetually:</i> - +continually, for ever.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}